WEBVTT

00:02:00.240 --> 00:02:03.640
I share the goals
of the speakers you heard before.

00:02:05.520 --> 00:02:10.479
I did not choose to take up the pen,

00:02:11.560 --> 00:02:12.760
the brush,

00:02:13.600 --> 00:02:14.800
the camera.

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:18.600
I chose this instrument.

00:02:19.440 --> 00:02:21.960
I chose the gun.

00:02:23.040 --> 00:02:25.496
For you, and you heard already,

00:02:25.520 --> 00:02:31.280
being so close to this gun
may make you feel uneasy.